<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n28070j"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n28" href="#n28070j">N28 (VI.D.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n28all.htm#n28070j"> 70(j)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Nonpareils / Players snuff candles</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Tallow <mark>candles</mark> stuck into circular iron sconces hung above the stage, and were now and then <mark>snuffed by the players</mark> in the pauses of tragic soliloquies, whilst the audience refreshed itself between the acts with oranges and <mark>nonpareils</mark>. <small> J. Fitzgerald Molloy, <a name="JFMR1" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#JFMR1"><cite title="source">The Romance of the Irish Stage</cite></a> (1897) I 88f</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c11165j" href="c11all.htm#c11165j">VI.C.11:165(j)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
